    {
      "id": "project-1778657618841",
      "title": "K2 Plus",
      "description": "K2 Plus is a functional prototype for an AI-powered conference assistant device. The Android phone is embedded as the product’s main screen, presenting meeting information, agenda, sign-in, realtime AI interaction, and meeting minutes. A Wear OS smartwatch is used to simulate the detachable Agent Dial, enabling swipe navigation, voice input, gesture control, and meeting workflow triggers.\n\nThe project explores how AI voice interaction, embedded display interfaces, and physical controls can work together to create a more natural and hands-free meeting experience.",
